What you need to know:

Despite coronavirus grinding sporting activities to a halt the world over, NMG’s Sports Desk, under the guidance of Sports managing Editor Elias Makori, did not go to sleepThe print, online and TV desks went out of their way to deliver unique stories and their efforts were duly recognised as NMG journalists dominated the awardsIdah Waringa’s story, The football con, earned global recognition as the best in the investigative reporting category